title: Has anyone else had the issue of chrome stop auto suggestion on Pixel 5
content: All of a sudden today I cannot get any auto suggestion or my search to automatically search after I'm done speaking or typing on my Pixel 5 I called support for some other issues I was having with it this morning because this is actually a brand new one that I got the other day and when I switched all the stuff from my old five half of it came half of it didn't lots of things seem to not be there completely we know more and get that fixed and all of a sudden I noticed that if I'm searching for anything it doesn't have auto suggest at all and as soon as I'm done typing I have to hit search it doesn't auto search anymore
